		@see [`openfl.events.Event.CLOSE`](https://api.openfl.org/openfl/events/Event.html#CLOSE)

		@since 1.0.0
	**/
	public function closeDatePicker():Void {
		if (!this.open) {
			return;
		}
		this.popUpAdapter.close();
	}

